abstract: British authorities confirm three relatives of onetime Al Qaeda leader Osama bin Laden were among four people killed in private jet crash in southern England.
lead_paragraph: Family members of the former Qaeda leader Osama bin Laden were among four people killed in a private jet crash in southern England, a Saudi ambassador said.

headline.main: Plane Crash Kills Relatives of Bin Laden
